    public interface Value
extends Any
    AnyValue defines the interface for single value data classes such as Float, String etc.

    • Field Detail

      • RANK_UNKNOWN

        static final int RANK_UNKNOWN
        Relative rankings of the precision of each scalar value type. The higher the ranking, the greater the precision. RANK_CONVERT means that conversion should take place i.e. StringI would have a precision of RANK_CONVERT
